When the moderators banned the Italian gamer, the people in the vc got mad and started a revolution. Because of their stupidity, they screenshotted the members in vc and posted it in the announcement channel like they felt proud of it. Unfortunately this became the ultimate weapon for temmie, who is a person that likes to report people. Due to mass panic, Chiruno asked NakajimaRegulus to create a second server and force them to join there. while people are gathering at the second server, there was an argument whether the creation of the second server was necessary or not. He also gave the ownership to brokski to evade his account suspension.
